      <title>市场综述：关税报告推动美元下跌，中国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有消息称，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的经济团队成员讨论了逐步提高关税以避免通胀飙升的方法，美国股指期货上涨，美元走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 22:37:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛杉矶山火给保险业造成的损失可能超过 300 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/la-wildfires-insurance-cost-estimates-spike-to-30-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肆虐洛杉矶大片地区的山火可能给保险业造成高达 300 亿美元的损失，因为火势在燃烧近一周后仍在肆虐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/la-wildfires-insurance-cost-estimates-spike-to-30-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 21:25:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克利夫兰克利夫斯和纽柯考虑联合竞购美国钢铁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/cleveland-cliffs-and-nucor-said-to-consider-joint-us-steel-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，克利夫兰-克利夫斯公司正与纽柯公司合作，考虑联合竞购美国钢铁公司。克利夫兰-克利夫斯公司的高层后来在新闻发布会上证实了他对这家美国钢铁制造商的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/cleveland-cliffs-and-nucor-said-to-consider-joint-us-steel-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:31:14 GMT</pubDate>
